Ranger Help for: aim
====================

SYNTAX:      aim <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     variable

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to take careful aim with a bow at a target
that is not currently in combat. The longer the Ranger aims, the more
damage the shot will deal when released. Aim is interrupted if the
Ranger moves, is attacked, or enters combat. The SP cost scales with
the time spent aiming. Requires a bow to be wielded and an arrow to
be readied.
